{"tid":718781,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"岡比亞總統警告中國，你攻台我就出兵！","createTime":"2018-06-27T03:15:05.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-27T05:47:04.000Z","uid":51701,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"b07b505a6a77647900288d2efd574d375888c514","tid":718781,"uid":51701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-27T03:15:05.000Z","msg":"全球華人資訊/薛毓砮<br />\n<br />\n日前，在美國訪問的岡比亞總統葉海亞-賈梅與布什會談中表示，一旦台海局勢發生變化，岡比亞將出兵中國攻擊中國沿海經濟區，以防止台海局勢擴大化。葉海亞 -賈梅聲稱，岡比亞只需派遣1000人左右的海軍陸戰隊就可以完全遏制中國的軍事行動。岡比亞總統葉海亞-賈梅不久前還宣佈他在夢中學會了治療艾滋病的方法。岡比亞是目前中華民國的24個建交國家之一 <br />\n<br />\n在美國訪問的岡比亞總統葉海亞-賈梅與布會談中曾經表示，一旦台海局勢發生變化，岡比亞將出兵中國攻擊中國沿海經濟區，以防止台海局勢擴大化。 <br />\n<img src=\"http://img1.qq.com/news/pics/4721/4721819.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg1.qq.com%2Fnews%2Fpics%2F4721%2F4721819.jpg&h=7d40c45a&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"http://img1.qq.com/news/pics/4721/4721821.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg1.qq.com%2Fnews%2Fpics%2F4721%2F4721821.jpg&h=9728e32a&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"http://img1.qq.com/news/pics/4721/4721823.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg1.qq.com%2Fnews%2Fpics%2F4721%2F4721823.jpg&h=d50de457&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"95b16df34d5deb624d35fceac03112fc4177cc2f","tid":718781,"uid":51701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-27T03:23:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2cd35c70528f165e04ca08e9f22bc98df89e5970","tid":718781,"uid":51701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-27T05:47:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}